snippet.title: Naruto Ultimate Ninja Heroes 2: The Phantom Fortress Trailer
snippet.description: The first trailer for the sequel to Naruto Ultimate Ninja Heroes. "Naruto Ultimate Ninja Heroes 2: The Phantom Fortress" is schedueled to arrive June 2008.
